{"type":null,"faqId":47191,"title":"忘记了屏幕解锁密码或图案","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:#333333;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.3048611in;}\n.s3{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.40347221in;}\n.s4{font-weight:bold;color:#333333;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Book Antiqua;font-size:9pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:9pt;}\n.p4{text-indent:-0.2951389in;margin-left:1.4763889in;margin-top:0.055555556in;margin-bottom:0.055555556in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.1930555in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">可以通过升级手机的方法解决。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=175531\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">升级后，手机内部存储中的数据将被删除。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">请根据手机的支持情况选择一种升级方式。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span class=\"s1\">通过 microSD 卡升级：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">步骤 1  </span><span class=\"s1\">进入</span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/downloads/index.htm%22 \\o %22 \"><span class=\"s1\">华为官网软件下载地址</span></a><span class=\"s1\">，根据手机型号下载软件升级包。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">步骤 2  </span><span class=\"s1\">将升级包中的 dload 文件夹放入 microSD 卡根目录下。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">步骤 3  </span><span class=\"s1\">在关机状态下，插入 microSD 卡。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">步骤 4  </span><span class=\"s1\">同时按住电源键和音量上下键直到出现安卓机器人图标。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">手机进入升级模式开始升级，升级完成后手机将恢复出厂设置。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<span class=\"s2\">  </span><span class=\"s1\">通过外接存储设备升级：</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">步骤 1  </span><span class=\"s1\">进入</span><a href=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/cn/support/downloads/index.htm%22 \\o %22 \"><span class=\"s1\">华为官网软件下载地址</span></a><span class=\"s1\">，根据手机型号下载软件升级包。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">步骤 2  </span><span class=\"s1\">将升级包中的 dload</span><span class=\"s4\"> </span><span class=\"s1\">文件夹放入 U 盘根目录下。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span class=\"s3\">步骤 3  </span><span class=\"s1\">同时按住电源键和音量上下键直到出现安卓机器人图标，手机自动进入升级模式开始升级。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">若无法升级，请联系客服或携带购机发票前往服务网点检修。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"2758","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445219090000,"seriesProductName":"TIT-AL00,TIT-CL10,TIT-TL00","visitedTimes":389,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"忘记密码,屏幕解锁密码,忘记图案,忘记绘图","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}